name: Summer Reading - original collage artwork
description:
An engraving of Henry Fielding layered on antique papers with paint and pen.

	Dimensions are 5” x 7 ” or 13 cm x 18 cm

	This is an original work of art, not a print.

	This work has been assembled on acid-free archival illustration board, and has been sealed with gloss varnish for protection. All of my works on illustration board come in a cellophane envelope.

name: Picture Tubes -- original collage artwork
description:
A brightly-coloured bird is layered with overpainted vintage papers, including an illustration and text from a 1953 television service manual.
This is an original work of art, not a print.

	Dimensions are 5” x 7 ” or 13 cm x 18 cm

	This work has been assembled on acid-free archival illustration board, and has been sealed with three coats of varnish for protection.

name: Eleanor Powell -- original collage artwork
description:
An overpainted and collaged photo of golden age movie actress and great dancer Eleanor Powell.

	Bonus Eleanor Powell quotation: “What we are is God’s gift to us. What we become is our gift to God.”

	This is an original work of art, not a print.

	Dimensions are 5” x 7 ” or 13 cm x 18 cm

	This work has been assembled on acid-free stretched artists canvas, with painted sides (ready for hanging), and has been sealed with three coats of gloss varnish for protection.

name: Valse -- original ACEO minature artwork collage
description: A little brown bird combined with old and modern papers and found text. This is an original, not a print. Size: 3 1/2” x 2 1/2” (or 9 cm x 6.5 cm) This ACEO has been prepared on acid-free illustration board and has been given several coats of gloss varnish for protection. What are ACEOs? ACEOs (Art Cards, Editions and Originals) are miniature works of art the size of a trading or playing card. People collect them and trade them.

name: Carole Lombard -- original collage artwork
description:
An image of movie star Carole Lombard overpainted and altered.

	This is an original work of art, not a print.

	Dimensions are 5” x 7 ” or 13 cm x 18 cm

	This work has been assembled on acid-free stretched canvas, painted on the sides, and can be displayed without framing.
